Moreover, the Company has established guidelines for business Code of Conduct, serving as the foundation for the conduct of Company personnel in line with the principles of good corporate governance. These guidelines are detailed in the Decree of Board of  Directors  No.  002/AI/SK-DIRSUS/VI/2022  on  Guidelines  for Implementing Business Code of Conduct of PT Acset Indonusa Tbk and ACSET Group. The decree contains the commitment of Company's Code of Conduct, including the following points:

